"Off → nothing recorded. Activity → metadata only (host, status, latency, swap report, leak warnings). AI request details → also captures bodies for known LLM hosts (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, Cohere, Mistral, Perplexity, x.ai, Groq, Replicate, HuggingFace). Everything → bodies for every host. Bodies are AES-GCM encrypted with the same keychain key as profile secrets. View at App → Trace Inspector (⇧⌘I)." = "Off → no se registra nada. Actividad → solo metadatos (host, estado, latencia, informe de swap, advertencias de fugas). Detalles de solicitudes IA → también captura los cuerpos para hosts LLM conocidos (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, Cohere, Mistral, Perplexity, x.ai, Groq, Replicate, HuggingFace). Todo → cuerpos para todos los hosts. Los cuerpos se cifran con AES-GCM con la misma clave del llavero que los secretos del perfil. Ver en App → Trace Inspector (⇧⌘I).";
